text: Michelle Kearley is a former Australian child actress. She was cast for the lead role of Molly Wilson in the Australian children's television series Sugar and Spice and as student Jessie Ross for seven episodes of the Australian soap opera Neighbours in 1988.Neighbours, Guest Character Profiles, Jessie Ross == References == == External links == * Category:Australian child actresses Category:Australian television actresses Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Living people
